//GRG PVE-Player-Markers-for-Epoch//
	
//Step 1;

	Download the file "PVE-Player-Markers-for-Epoch" and extract it to your documents.
	
	Unpack your MPMission - epoch.Altis.pbo (Changes dependable on the map you are using).

//Step 2;
	
	Merge the contents of the EPOCH_custom_OnEachFrame.sqf file with the same file in your MPMission file which can be located at: "epoch.Altis\epoch_code\customs\EPOCH_custom_OnEachFrame.sqf".
	
//Step 3;

	Repack your file and upload to your server.
	
	Restart your server and ensure no errors are present in your RPT.

Additional scripts are avalible from GhostriderGaming [GRG] - Find the link at the top of this file!

	
